# Backend Rules

Stack:
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- Firebase Auth verification

Architecture:

routes/
services/
repositories/
schemas/

Rules:

- Business logic must live in services.
- Routes must remain thin.
- Database access only via repository layer.

API Principles:
- Response must be deterministic.
- Always return typed schema responses.
- Validate inputs using Pydantic.

Performance:
- Prefer simple queries over premature optimization.
